{"tid":1529373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家 破壞完就走 唔好再打陣地 你地無將黑警往死裡打嘅鬥志 就輸","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T18:45:35.000Z","uid":119262,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"72776404c6ea661aa5a90cc820b959a203b3f7e4","tid":1529373,"uid":119262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"咁耐以黎 我地贏在人多 流動性大<br />\n好似今日東涌站咁 拆完就走 <br />\n已經有好大效果<br />\n<br />\n打陣地 淨係set road block係 <span style=\"color: red;\">無 可 能 贏</span><br />\n要贏要個個都有將黑警往死裡打嘅鬥志<br />\n當佢地係殺你全家嘅仇人 （佢地就係有咁嘅諗法）<br />\n但 唔 係 個 個 都 ready 好<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n點解仲要同佢地打消耗戰？<br />\n點解仲要正面衝突？<br />\n<br />\n嗌口號唔係唔得 但當大家都知我地嘅目標<br />\n留番啖氣去拆野係咪仲好<br />\n唔好再企係到送頭<br />\n<br />\n再 一 次 呼 籲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 唔好比你嘅敵人全身而退毫無損傷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 唔好再拉住自己友 除非佢衝去死</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要站邊一早站左 唔會因爲任何野嘅割席 <span style=\"color: blue;\">呢一點大家都清楚！</span></span>"},{"pid":"575c2db90afe77eaa1c1ac4d9fbcc6e8b697c553","tid":1529373,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f448ddf70d95b25c2d036556e5490f3f380d0113","tid":1529373,"uid":119262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c494b4f7c56b5781c4d9dd9895d727818c627919","tid":1529373,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"［學生入黎！］推到所有有暴力傾向嘅教蓄仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/152921